videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen dives to the floor to collect a loose ball, and on the other end Marvin Bagley III rises up for a one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Allen's hustle sets up Bagley slam

videos.description: Chaundee Brown gets the ball in the corner and drives to the hoop, tiptoeing along the baseline and getting by three Duke defenders to tie the game at 13-13.
videos.headline: Brown drives baseline for tough Wake basket

videos.description: Doral Moore outjumps a defender and punishes the rim with a big jam for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Moore hammers down one-handed putback dunk

videos.description: Alex O'Connell intercepts a pass and goes all the way to jam it home for Duke.
videos.headline: O'Connell turns steal into dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen's nice feed sets up a jam by Javin DeLaurier for Duke.
videos.headline: Allen finds DeLaurier for dunk

videos.description: Brandon Childress throws up a lob to Doral Moore who jams it home as the first half ends for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Childress connects with Moore on alley-oop

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III shows of his ball handling by taking it all way by himself for a jam.
videos.headline: Bagley goes to coast-to-coast for dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen makes a great pass while falling back to Marvin Bagley III for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Allen's great pass leads to Bagley slam

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets the loose ball and rockets it down court to Gary Trent Jr. who jams it home.
videos.headline: Allen's powerful pass leads to Trent dunk
